# Wildlife Watcher Model Conversion - Environment Variables

# Supabase Configuration
# Get these from your Supabase project settings: https://app.supabase.com/project/_/settings/api
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here
#
# INat OAuth
# TBP - I have added these to the env for now, they can also be hosted within streamlit with settings under secret
# but as we will migrate to a website eventually, this makes more sense:
# Option B (Streamlit Cloud): App Secrets
# On Streamlit Community Cloud, you don’t typically use .env. Instead set these in: Streamlit → Your app → Settings → Secrets

# Redirect URI must match exactly what you register in iNaturalist:
#   - Local dev:    http://localhost:8501/
#   - Streamlit:    https://wildlifewatcher.streamlit.app/
INAT_CLIENT_ID=your-inat-client-id
INAT_CLIENT_SECRET=your-inat-client-secret
INAT_REDIRECT_URI=http://localhost:8501/

# Optional: OAuth scope (default in code is "write")
# INAT_SCOPE=write
